fr.zelus.jarvis.intent

Interface IntentDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EObject, EventDefinition, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IntentDefinitionImpl

    public interface IntentDefinition
extends EventDefinition
    A representation of the model object 'Definition'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Follows
    • Followed By
    • In Contexts
    • Training Sentences
    See Also:
